♪You didn't hear♪

168
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:49,780
♪My last goodbye♪

169
00:08:50,490 --> 00:08:53,920
♪I walked away♪

170
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:57,250
♪With tears in my eye♪

171
00:08:57,250 --> 00:09:01,410
♪Actually, you have changed too♪

172
